\n\tThe driver lets you remap nearly every normally remappable key on the Control4 remote to any command in the document, and it would be trivial to add Back if it existed in the protocol.\n
"\n\tI'd *love* to add 'Back' to the current driver, if it's missing something I can add, but I'm not seeing it.\n"
\n\t"Back" is on the Bolt and keyboard remotes on the left side under Input, in the same location "Zoom" used to be (though the new remotes have a dedicated Zoom key on the right).\n
"\n\tIt's not documented, but maybe IRCODE BACK would work?\n"
