FIOS TV DVRs also don\'t have a specific "commercial skip" feature, but they do have a built-in 30-second skip and fully-featured fast forward, both of which work on pre-recorded programming and after pausing live TV, but not on Video On Demand programming. However, in some cases if you\'re using FIOS TV\'s multi-room DVR feature and watching recorded programming on a non-DVR box elsewhere in your home, 
". The fast forward button, however, does work wherever you're watching."
