"While playing a recorded show, hit select-play-select-3-0-select. You'll hear 3 chimes if you did it right. You'll need to redo this whenever the Tivo reboots."
ow, your "skip" button will skip 30 seconds, not to the next hash mark on your show\'s progress bar. 
Wired reports that this still works too
", and confirms that if your TiVo loses power, gets a software update, or is rebooted, you'll have to repeat the above command to get the 30-second skip functionality back. The skip feature does not work on live TV."
"With luck, there's a skip button or feature for your DVR in the list above, or it already comes with a button that allows you to quickly fast forward or skip 30 seconds at a time without hassle. However, you'll notice we didn't mention some providers, most notably Time Warner, who actually "
