With the touch of a button, skip to the end of a commercial break and resume watching instantly. Introducing SkipMode.
he SkipMode feature is available only on certain recorded shows; we hope to make it available for the most popular shows on the most popular channels watched by TiVo subscribers. That means you\xe2\x80\x99ll find SkipMode availability on many shows that you record between 4:30 p.m. and midnight (or 12:30 a.m. on major networks) on the most widely-watched channels. \xc2\xa0
When you get to the end of a show segment, press the 
\xc2\xa0button or CHANNEL UP on your remote.
\xc2\xa0You\xe2\x80\x99re at the beginning of the next segment, without a commercial in sight.
t any time during the show, CHANNEL UP takes you to the next show segment. For instance, want to skip the judging on your favorite reality show competition (like The Voice or Dancing with the Stars)? Just press CHANNEL UP when the judging starts. You\xe2\x80\x99ll skip past the judging and though the next commercial break. Your show will start playing at the beginning of the next segment.
o skip back to the beginning of a previous show segment, press CHANNEL DOWN.
Want to know more about how SkipMode works? Check out the full 
